  <entry>
    <title>面试手写函数1</title>
    <url>/2020/04/11/%E9%9D%A2%E8%AF%95%E6%89%8B%E5%86%99%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B01/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>记录一下最近一段时间，参与春招面试碰到的手写函数，巩固一下自己的基础。</p>
<h3 id="数组去重"><a href="#数组去重" class="headerlink" title="数组去重"></a>数组去重</h3><p>数组去重本来是很容易的，特别是有了Set对象后(arr为要去重的数组)</p>
<figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[...new <span class="built_in">Set</span>(arr)]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>但是如果加上附加条件、要求性能就挺麻烦了。</p>
<p>es5大多数解法是通过一个Map记录数组的每一项，然后便利数组，没有重复的就记录下来，只需要一次遍历。</p>
<p>如果要求在原数组中操作呢？那么删除元素就只有通过splice方法，但是如果对于数组中有1万个0或者[1,1,2,2,3,3,4,4…]，这种数组，一个个删除的效率太低，可以通过冒泡的方法把非重复项移到数组前面，然后截尾即可。</p>
<figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">uniqBy = <span class="function">(<span class="params">arr</span>) =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">let</span> map = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="built_in">Map</span>();</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">let</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>;    </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">let</span> j=<span class="number">0</span>; j &lt; arr.length; j++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">if</span> (!map.has(arr[j])) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        i != j &amp;&amp; ([arr[i], arr[j]] = [arr[j], arr[i]]);</span><br><span class="line">        map.set(arr[i++], <span class="literal">true</span>);</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;    </span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  arr.splice(i, arr.length - i)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>那如果数组中的每一项都是对象呢？比如：</p>
<figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">let</span> singers = [</span><br><span class="line">    &#123; <span class="attr">id</span>: <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="attr">name</span>: <span class="string">'Leslie Cheung'</span> &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">    &#123; <span class="attr">id</span>: <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="attr">name</span>: <span class="string">'Leslie Cheung'</span> &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">    &#123; <span class="attr">id</span>: <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="attr">name</span>: <span class="string">'Eason Chan'</span> &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>一样也是有骚操作的</p>
<figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">uniqBy = <span class="function">(<span class="params">arr, key</span>) =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">return</span> [...new <span class="built_in">Map</span>(arr.map(<span class="function"><span class="params">item</span>=&gt;</span>[item[key],item])).values()]</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>一样有不依靠骚操作版本</p>
<figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">uniqBy = <span class="function">(<span class="params">arr, key</span>) =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">let</span> map = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="built_in">Map</span>();</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">let</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>;    </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">let</span> j=<span class="number">0</span>; j &lt; arr.length; j++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">if</span> (!map.has(arr[j][key])) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        i != j &amp;&amp; ([arr[i], arr[j]] = [arr[j], arr[i]]);</span><br><span class="line">        map.set(arr[i][key], i++);</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;    </span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  arr.splice(i, arr.length - i)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
      <tags>
        <tag>学习</tag>
        <tag>前端</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>js深拷贝</title>
    <url>/2020/04/10/js%E6%B7%B1%E6%8B%B7%E8%B4%9D/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="深拷贝还是浅拷贝"><a href="#深拷贝还是浅拷贝" class="headerlink" title="深拷贝还是浅拷贝"></a>深拷贝还是浅拷贝</h1><p>深拷贝和浅拷贝的问题，我在第一次参加秋招面试的时候就碰上了，我当时的回答现在已经记不得了，面试之后我看了几个版本的深、浅拷贝代码，觉得不是很难。后来多看了几回自称完美的方案之后，反倒是觉得没有完美的深拷贝方案。</p>
<h3 id="浅拷贝"><a href="#浅拷贝" class="headerlink" title="浅拷贝"></a>浅拷贝</h3><p>（浅拷贝非常简单，第一层属性值如果是引用类型，只拷贝引用）</p>
<figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">shallowClone</span>(<span class="params">o</span>)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">if</span>( (<span class="keyword">typeof</span> o !== <span class="string">'object'</span> &amp;&amp; <span class="keyword">typeof</span> o !== <span class="string">'function'</span>) || o === <span class="literal">null</span>)</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">return</span> o;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">let</span> obj;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">if</span>(o <span class="keyword">instanceof</span> <span class="built_in">Array</span>)</span><br><span class="line">		obj = [];</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">		obj = &#123;&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="keyword">let</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> o)</span><br><span class="line">		obj[i] = o[i];</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">return</span> obj;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>有几个骚操作，在参考【1】中看到的，</p>
<figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">obj2 = <span class="built_in">Object</span>.assign(&#123;&#125;, obj1)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;...obj2&#125; &#x3D; obj1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;仅限数组</span><br><span class="line">arr2 &#x3D; arr1.slice(0);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;同仅限数组</span><br><span class="line">arr2 &#x3D; [].concat(arr1);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<blockquote>
<p>实际上对于数组来说， 只要不修改原数组， 重新返回一个新数组就可以实现浅拷贝，比如说map、filter、reduce等方法</p>
<p>摘自参考【1】</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="深拷贝"><a href="#深拷贝" class="headerlink" title="深拷贝"></a>深拷贝</h3><blockquote>
<p>一般来说 JS 深克隆要考虑下面几个问题：</p>
<p>JSON 克隆不支持函数、引用、undefined、Date、RegExp 等<br>递归克隆要考虑环、爆栈<br>要考虑 Date、RegExp、Function 等特殊对象的克隆方式<br>要不要克隆 <strong>proto</strong>，如果要克隆，就非常浪费内存；如果不克隆，就不是深克隆。</p>
<p>摘自参考【2】</p>
</blockquote>
<p>因为上述问题的存在，尤其是proto的问题，导致真正意义上的深拷贝很难，递归克隆、Date、RegExp、Function、Error都还有解决的办法，虽然Function的办法依然不完美，使用bind方法（参考【3】）得到的函数本质上还是用了拷贝引用</p>
<h5 id="暴力不负责实现"><a href="#暴力不负责实现" class="headerlink" title="暴力不负责实现"></a>暴力不负责实现</h5><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">JSON</span>.parse( <span class="built_in">JSON</span>.stringify(obj))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>缺点（摘自参考【1】）：</p>
<ol>
<li>会忽略 undefined</li>
<li>会忽略 symbol</li>
<li>不能序列化函数</li>
<li>不能解决循环引用的对象</li>
<li>不能正确处理new Date()</li>
<li>不能处理正则</li>
<li>不能处理new Error()</li>
<li>会抛弃对象的constructor,所有的构造函数会指向Object【参考4】</li>
</ol>
<h5 id="较为完善解法"><a href="#较为完善解法" class="headerlink" title="较为完善解法"></a>较为完善解法</h5><p>先上代码（代码主要来自参考【1】，懒，只添加了函数判断、cache.filter换成的find方法）</p>
<figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">deepCopy</span>(<span class="params">obj, cache = []</span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">if</span> (obj === <span class="literal">null</span> || (<span class="keyword">typeof</span> obj !== <span class="string">'object'</span> &amp;&amp; <span class="keyword">typeof</span> obj !== <span class="string">'function'</span>)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> obj</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="built_in">Object</span>.prototype.toString.call(obj) === <span class="string">'[object Date]'</span>) <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="built_in">Date</span>(obj)</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="built_in">Object</span>.prototype.toString.call(obj) === <span class="string">'[object RegExp]'</span>) <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="built_in">RegExp</span>(obj)</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="built_in">Object</span>.prototype.toString.call(obj) === <span class="string">'[object Error]'</span>) <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="built_in">Error</span>(obj)</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="keyword">typeof</span> obj === <span class="string">'function'</span>) <span class="keyword">return</span> obj.bind(&#123;&#125;);</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">const</span> item = cache.find(<span class="function"><span class="params">item</span> =&gt;</span> item.original === obj)</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">if</span> (item) <span class="keyword">return</span> item.copy</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">let</span> copy = <span class="built_in">Array</span>.isArray(obj) ? [] : &#123;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">  cache.push(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    original: obj,</span><br><span class="line">    copy</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">Object</span>.keys(obj).forEach(<span class="function"><span class="params">key</span> =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    copy[key] = deepCopy(obj[key], cache)</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">return</span> copy</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>首先，如果变量是基本数据类型，直接返回原值</p>
<p>如果是特殊对象，Date、RegExp、Error，则通过原值新建变量，如果是Function，通过bind方式可以得到一个新函数，并且这里有一个矛盾</p>
<p>如果把函数真正意义上拷贝了下来，对比闭包中的函数怎么解决变量引用的问题？我目前没有了解到js中提供闭包内函数对父级函数的引用</p>
<p>由于bind本质上是在对象上添加了函数的索引，然后再通过对象调用函数的方法实现了修改this指针，因此还是是使用了函数引用，因此闭包可以正常访问</p>
<p>对于递归引用的问题，使用了数组记录所有拷贝过的对象，如果有重复引用，就直接返回拷贝过的值。除了数组，还可以用Map记录</p>
<p>缺点：</p>
<ol>
<li>依然没有拷贝proto</li>
<li>Function拷贝不完美</li>
</ol>
<p>如果有更好的办法，还会继续更新</p>
<p>挖个坑，有时间学习</p>
<p><a href="https://juejin.im/post/5df7175fe51d45582512962c" target="_blank" rel="noopener">头条面试官：你知道如何实现高性能版本的深拷贝嘛？</a></p>
<p>参考：</p>
<p>【1】<a href="https://juejin.im/post/5e906ab8518825738e217414" target="_blank" rel="noopener">JavaScript系列： 一、手撕JS中的深浅拷贝</a></p>
<p>【2】<a href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/64703741/answer/223375284" target="_blank" rel="noopener">JavaScript深克隆-方应杭-知乎回答</a></p>
<p>【3】<a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/1833588/javascript-clone-a-function" target="_blank" rel="noopener">bind方法拷贝函数</a></p>
<p>【4】<a href="https://juejin.im/post/5abb55ee6fb9a028e33b7e0a" target="_blank" rel="noopener">面试官:请你实现一个深克隆</a></p>
]]></content>
